time complexity: O(C(n,k) * k)
space complexity: O(k)
energy implications: LOW
explanation: Uses depth-first backtracking with pruning to generate combinations in lexicographic order. The pruning condition i <= n - (k - cur.size()) + 1 avoids exploring branches that cannot yield enough remaining elements, cutting the search space significantly.

